2) Pairwise local feature learning based on CNNs: We have established CNNs to learn the local features of circRNAdisease node pairs. In the CNNs, each block consists of a convolution layer followed by a pooling layer. In the l-th block (1 ⩽ l ⩽ D), given the feature representation of a circRNAdisease node pair Y (l−1)
