3) Adaptive fusion of pairwise local features and global features: The pairwise local feature representation YLoc and global feature representation YGlo hold varying degrees of importance for the feature representation learning of each circRNA (disease) node. We assign a learnable weight parameter sβ for YGlo and sγ for YLoc, and after normalization, we obtain β and γ,
β = esβ
